title: Howard Stern Radio Show 2001 - All shows
description:
All of the howard stern radio show from 2001.
The audio quality is garbage, and the files are malformed. (multiple files concatinated together)

They were all I could find, and they seem to be from the defunct wushdismeen fan site.
Some guy deleted this torrent fromso I'm putting it up here. Please seed, I'd like to see this stay alive.


If you know where I can find a better set of recordings (these are mono, 30kbs mp3 files, contain ads, and skip occasionally) please let me know so I can get them.




before listening, I re-encoded all of the files with these settings (so my iPod could play them right) The files I'm seeding are untouched

mkdir re-encode;
cd re-encode;
for F in ...mp3 ; do ffmpeg -i "$F" -q 4  $(basename "$F") ; done
